      • partSearchKeyTyped

        void partSearchKeyTyped​(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent event)
        Searches the Inventory for any part name or ID that at least partially matches the search string.

        Each time the user presses a key this updates the listing of parts found in partsTable.

        If search string is null, all parts are displayed.

        Parameters:
        event - user generated event (a key pressed) that caused this to execute

      • productSearchKeyTyped

        void productSearchKeyTyped​(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent event)
        Searches the Inventory for any product name or ID that at least partially matches the search string.

        Each time the user presses a key this updates the listing of products found in productsTable.

        If search string is null, all products are displayed.

        Parameters:
        event - user generated event (a key pressed) that caused this to execute
